code: public String[] formatScope(TaskMetricGroup parent, OperatorID operatorID, String operatorName) {     final String[] template = copyTemplate().     final String[] values = { parent.parent().parent().hostname(), parent.parent().parent().taskManagerId(), valueOrNull(parent.parent().jobId()), valueOrNull(parent.parent().jobName()), valueOrNull(parent.vertexId()), valueOrNull(parent.executionId()), valueOrNull(parent.taskName()), String.valueOf(parent.subtaskIndex()), String.valueOf(parent.attemptNumber()), valueOrNull(operatorID), valueOrNull(operatorName) }.     return bindVariables(template, values). }
